{"tid":1909474,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"樓上鑽撚完未呀","createTime":"2020-03-04T03:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T08:45:10.000Z","uid":154012,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"57b314ab68ac14c75b6b89b8433c5f85747de354","tid":1909474,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"朝朝準時夠鐘就鑽<br />\n日日都比呢d鑽鑽鑽鑽鑽聲嘈聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n裝修要時間我明<br />\n但樓上三日唔埋都係度裝修咁 無停過<br />\n鑽左幾年啦屌 起棟樓都起到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日頭就鑽 夜晚就係度揼<br />\n每次同管理處投訴完  好啦 停左手<br />\n過一排又繼續<br />\ndllm 係咪咁撚多野鑽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成間屋都感受到個震動<br />\n聽住鑽鑽聲開po真係零捨有感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唉 好撚嘈呀"},{"pid":"f856df42023c6fa1592385421a49c21a9672facf","tid":1909474,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"有冇上樓拍門？"},{"pid":"a17c221f6edcceda5c988f00c4383bdcbeac62db","tid":1909474,"uid":101589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:53:55.000Z","msg":"試下上樓咁有氣勢屌7佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09e8b1565239137e30c261b804abf0cbdba1b764","tid":1909474,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:55:22.000Z","msg":"買振樓神器啦"},{"pid":"7d86106a38d286702b06bf01b2171bc6251a7130","tid":1909474,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f856df42023c6fa1592385421a49c21a9672facf","tid":1909474,"uid":60000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:52:04.000Z","msg":"有冇上樓拍門？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T03:58:40.000Z","msg":"有上過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f6d7679788fe548afbee86dd0d79eb71b43e94","tid":1909474,"uid":154012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a17c221f6edcceda5c988f00c4383bdc